---
title: Paprika Salmon in a Lemony Sauce with Pistachio Rice & Roasted Carrots
description: Lemon brightens up any meal, and this dish is positively bursting with citrusy goodness! Paprika-coated chicken is drizzled with a creamy, lemon-and-thyme-spiked pan sauce that’d taste good on pretty much anything. On the side; tender roasted carrots and steamy rice with lemon zest and pistachios. When life gives you lemons, you know what to do.
